@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
[*] --> Completed
Completed --> Created : confirm
Created --> OnHold : submit
Created : entry / log package
OnHold --> Delivered : submit
Delivered --> Processing : approve
Processing --> Archived : confirm
Processing : entry / log package
Archived --> [*]
@enduml